Hi DDCControl team!

Thanks for the utility, it works great. So glad to be able to control my
monitor brightness programmatically!

DDCControl says that my monitor isn't in it's db, I *am* on an older ubuntu
so maybe I'm just out of date and if that's the case I'm sorry to have
bothered you.

My LANG= LC_ALL= ddccontrol -p -c -d output is attached.

I hope it's useful.

Again, many thanks.
- Dan

